premise_source_doc_sentence: Gravity premiered at the 70th Venice International Film Festival on August 28 , 2013 where it won the Future Film Festival Digital Award .
Gravity opened the 70th Venice International Film Festival on August 28 , 2013 and had its North American premiere three days later at the Telluride Film Festival .
The film became the eighth-highest-grossing film of 2013 with a worldwide gross of over against production budget of only $ 100 million .
Both the American Film Institute and National Board of Review included the film in their list of top ten films of 2013 .
Gravity is a 2013 3D science-fiction thriller film directed , co-produced , co-written , and co-edited by Alfonso Cuarón .
